characterDescription.skinTone: Light olive skin with warm golden undertones and a noticeable amount of freckles concentrated around the nose and cheeks; slightly uneven pigmentation with some redness, especially near the chin.
characterDescription.eyeColor: Hazel-green eyes with a prominent darker green limbal ring and subtle amber flecks around the pupil.
characterDescription.eyeShape: Almond-shaped eyes with slightly downturned outer corners and moderate eyelid exposure.
characterDescription.hairColor: Dark chestnut brown with lighter warm brown highlights and undertones.
characterDescription.hairTexture: Slightly wavy with natural volume and a somewhat coarse texture.
characterDescription.hairStyle: Long hair past the shoulders, parted slightly off-center to the right with face-framing layers.
characterDescription.faceShape: Oval face with soft, full cheeks and a gently rounded jawline.
characterDescription.nose: Medium-sized nose with a straight bridge and a slightly rounded tip.
characterDescription.lips: Medium-sized lips with a slightly fuller bottom lip and a natural pink hue.
characterDescription.smile: Gentle, closed-lip smile with a slight upward turn at the corners of the mouth; teeth are not visible.
characterDescription.eyebrows: Medium-thick, dark brown eyebrows with a natural arch and a well-defined shape.
characterDescription.ears: Ears are not fully visible, but appear to be medium-sized and positioned close to the head.
characterDescription.cheeks: Full cheeks with slight rosiness, especially noticeable when smiling.
characterDescription.chin: Rounded soft chin with a smooth contour.
characterDescription.facialProportions: Balanced facial proportions with eyes taking up approximately 1/5th of the face vertically, nose approximately 1/3rd of the vertical face length.
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: Extensive freckles distributed across the face, primarily concentrated on the nose and cheek areas. The subject also shows some acne scarring near the chin. There is a slightly visible line between the eyebrows
characterDescription.overallImpression: Appears approachable and friendly, with a natural and slightly worn appearance.
characterDescription.fullDescription: The subject is a woman between 30 and 35 years old with light olive skin, warmed by golden undertones and covered in a generous spattering of freckles, which are most dense around the nose and cheeks. Her eyes are hazel-green, rimmed with a darker green limbal ring and subtly flecked with amber closest to the pupils. She has long, slightly wavy dark chestnut brown hair with warm brown highlights, parted a little to the right. She has an oval face with soft, full cheeks, and medium lips in a gentle, closed-lip smile and acne scarring near the chin
